name: Ashley_42-inch_Wood_Wall-mount_Cabinet
description:
This Ashley cabinet mounts on the wall with built-in cleats inside for an easy installation. This wall-mount shelving unit is perfect as a medicine cabinet, spice cabinet, or storage cabinet anywhere. 
Includes: One (1) wall-mount cabinetMaterials: Solid pine, glassFinish: Natural pine finish can be painted or stainedShelves: Four (4) fully adjustable glass shelvesShaker style door sits on concealed hingesDoor is left undrilled for a knob or handle so you can mount it to open either directionCabinet portion is 22.5 inches high insideOpen shelf is 16.25 inches high insideApproximately: 7.25 inches deep inside the cabinetDimensions: 49.5 inches high x 15.25 inches wide x  8 inches deepMaterialWoodTypeWall CabinetFinishWood Finish
